text: In the Advanced tab, you can configure the advanced XML binding options. Open See the text in the Properties field for further information about the XML binding options. Caution! If possible, avoid renaming. If you must rename the profile, it has to be saved again in its new location, regenerating the UDRs there. For further information about viewing the UDR type structure, see Web Service UDR Type Folder Structure .
